**Pattern**: Simple Agent (Single-agent)
**Type**: Foundational
**Framework Support**: Google ADK (LlmAgent), CrewAI (Agent)

**Key Characteristics**:
- **Atomic Unit**: One agent, one task, zero complexity
- **Deterministic**: Well-defined inputs and outputs
- **Stateless**: No memory between interactions
- **Direct**: Straight-line execution path

**Business Value**:
- **Reliability**: Predictable, consistent outputs
- **Fast Deployment**: Quick to implement and test
- **Easy Maintenance**: Simple to debug and update
- **Cost Effective**: Minimal computational overhead

**Use Cases**:
- Automated documentation generation
- Report generation
- Customer service responses
- Document processing
- API documentation sync

**Real Example**:
TechCorp automated API documentation generation, achieving 92% reduction in documentation lag and $180K annual savings in engineering time.

**When to Use**:
- Repetitive, well-defined tasks
- Clear success criteria
- Reliability over sophistication
- Quick wins needed
- No complex state management required
